comments: Durant (BKN) and George (LAC) make incidental contact after Durant makes the pass.
Irving (BKN) makes contact to Morris Sr.'s (LAC) body during his driving shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) has his off-arm extended when he makes contact to Morris Sr's (LAC) face.
Durant (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Leonard (LAC).
Jackson (LAC) makes contact to the body of Irving (BKN) at the start of his drive that affects his SQBR.
George (LAC) makes contact with Durant's (BKN) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Durant (BKN) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
Jackson (LAC) makes contact to Green's (BKN) arm/body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) commits a take foul on Batum (LAC).
Leonard (LAC) makes contact to Irving's (BKN) lower body that affects his SQBR, but the foul is whistled on George (LAC), who makes clean contact with the ball and avoids making contact with Irving.
